snippet.title: Jared Leto & Amber Heard Join The Snyder Cut! The Arrowverse, What To Expect? Weekly Geekly Podcast!
snippet.description:
New format, LIVE and direct with a special guest! 
This weeks guest, Shaun Stackhouse.
You can find him at his channel  - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6Pj4tobwjFhSxq4E1aJXdw

Please join in on the chat with us!

Topics
5:50 New Batwoman In DC Comics FIRST
13:35 Jared Leto & Amber Heard Return As Part Of Snyder Cut Reshoots
31:30 Is The Ayer Cut Real? Will It Make A Debut On HBO Max?
41:30 NYC Re-Opens Theaters, What Does This Mean For Comic Book Films?
53:00 HBO Max The Future For DC TV Shows?
